{"tid":1285901,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想自殺個啲真係蠢過豬兜","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T19:10:50.000Z","uid":248699,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e740040c4cdedb61f547468e511b3a39bea6a3c9","tid":1285901,"uid":248699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:16:30.000Z","msg":"屌你你自殺咪即係中林鄭計<br />\n佢最開心就係見到你班傻仔自動消失 無曬所有反對聲音<br />\n仲有你班話想死嘅仆街 我唔理你真係情緒好差好灰又好 純粹呃關注又好<br />\n屌你一句話想死 搞到我班朋友尋晚搵你搵通宵<br />\n<br />\n如果你情緒好唔得，唔該立即停止接受任何反送中消息，新聞，做其他事分散注意力<br />\n唔係真係想死又同人講想死，唔該你收皮<br />\n或者搵我，俾我屌打到你有翻人生團火<br />\n屌你老母你嘅死唔係偉大，係自私！"},{"pid":"61f38a8c639d67bd3cdffe6940dc69f5b4d47846","tid":1285901,"uid":248699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"利申： 尊重並希望任何已過世的人士能得到釋懷，以上言論純屬針對依加想自殺嘅人"},{"pid":"d97693d7dc1fd70f97a64869f73570efdceb5a8e","tid":1285901,"uid":248699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:26:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1de18ba333a86bdcfe902abf2c4b128d79b01364","tid":1285901,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"面對敵人既方法就係同佢鬥長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a8416623749b4256cf4fbdb3ad809df5636cda","tid":1285901,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:34:37.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"44b4e7bf954cc74707d7093e02482f9a03b7b4c5","tid":1285901,"uid":83002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:47:20.000Z","msg":"<code>屌醒佢地</code>"},{"pid":"ec361adb779077d442c79116de60690fceb7e265","tid":1285901,"uid":266986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:00:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e739e51987e34001e8b451f5c6a580174940b06","tid":1285901,"uid":248699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:10:50.000Z","msg":"屌又有人嗌要死 屌你老母快啲搵我傾"}]}